Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.10,0:02:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求。。求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.56,0:02:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要錢的話多少都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.37,0:02:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以只要我的命。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.04,0:02:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的。。腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.55,0:02:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.76,0:02:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第六話\N黑夜來的訪問者黑笠現身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.42,0:03:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣各位覺得如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.23,0:03:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣了？\N這可是我捲起袖子做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.16,0:03:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總該表示些意見吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.83,0:03:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊。左之助也真是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.37,0:03:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好吃了\N都流出口水來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.54,0:03:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.91,0:03:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好難吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.91,0:03:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好苦喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.85,0:03:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好辣喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.85,0:03:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要哭了為了要生存\N必須要忍耐一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.05,0:03:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心每天都吃這個\N你也是很辛苦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.76,0:03:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，吃小熏小姐所做的菜\N能增加味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.50,0:03:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是很好的菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.33,0:03:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪裏好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.23,0:03:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有意見的話不要來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.24,0:03:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每天只是來吃飯的還敢有意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.67,0:04:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不找人打架後就沒錢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.71,0:04:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要說得小裏小氣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.11,0:04:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的！什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.45,0:04:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忽然闖進來真是對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.22,0:04:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.72,0:04:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警察署長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.26,0:04:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警察署長？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.49,0:04:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位\N前些日子增加各位的麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.46,0:04:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼今天有什麼事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.50,0:04:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村先生今天我是來\N拜託你一件事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.78,0:04:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這關係到政府的威信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.15,0:04:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十年前\N新聞也把這件事封鎖起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.58,0:04:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你\N請你把這個殺人魔打倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.42,0:04:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺人魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.18,0:05:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人稱黑笠是非常厲害的劍客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.55,0:05:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這十年\N那傢伙鎖定的目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.45,0:05:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是一些政府的大人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.12,0:05:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且他以前也是維新志士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.95,0:05:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前也是維新志士？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.59,0:05:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙先送警告書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.73,0:05:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後闖進來破壞警察的警備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.96,0:05:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺人對他來說\N簡直是一件快樂的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.90,0:05:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犧牲者之中\N也有很多的女性及小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.77,0:05:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這樣，為什麼不用槍打他呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.31,0:05:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然每回也配備了拳槍警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.61,0:05:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是還沒拔槍之前\N全員都被殺死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.12,0:05:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,槍還沒拔就被殺死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.13,0:06:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個叫黑笠的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.46,0:06:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怕跟小生一樣\N是之前幕府的殺人者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.94,0:06:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使明治過了十年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.10,0:06:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心已被血的顏色及味道所奪去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.61,0:06:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法停止殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.38,0:06:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不幸的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.03,0:07:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！時間快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.63,0:07:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上就是黑笠所警告的十二點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.70,0:07:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託各位了，殺了那傢伙的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.37,0:07:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會照各位所希望的錢付給你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.27,0:07:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請交給我們好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.71,0:07:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那黑笠來了\N我們會把他給殺了。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.18,0:07:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是討厭的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.91,0:07:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是為什麼連你也來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.95,0:07:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼玩意兒\N這麼有趣的打架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.32,0:07:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能只讓你一個人表現嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.39,0:07:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是打架吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.59,0:07:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是還沒拔槍\N全部都被殺死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.06,0:07:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這到底是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.43,0:07:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩，恐怕是。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.80,0:07:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想到什麼了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.70,0:07:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你心裏有什麼線索嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.53,0:07:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你該不會知道\N黑笠那傢伙的真正身份吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.40,0:07:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十二點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.61,0:07:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是警告的時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.96,0:08:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰。。是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.80,0:08:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.74,0:08:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不在裏面，在外面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.19,0:08:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了\N最前面由小生和左之助來防守
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.16,0:08:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其他的人跟在後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.72,0:09:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還。。沒來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.19,0:09:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是在裝腔作勢唬人而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.93,0:09:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿。。都在都在。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.44,0:09:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道命運的蟲也在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.47,0:09:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一。。二。。三。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.45,0:09:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十四，十五隻比想像中的還要少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.35,0:09:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個目眼。。太危陷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.82,0:09:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙由我來對付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.62,0:09:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谷大人拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.76,0:09:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快。快上！打倒那傢伙後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.06,0:09:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會付五倍的錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.53,0:09:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也會讓他做陸軍的仕官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.10,0:09:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五倍。。。！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.86,0:09:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了。。我接受！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.63,0:10:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也接受了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.40,0:10:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳東西\N為了慾望要捨棄生命嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.88,0:10:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩，這種感覺真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.88,0:10:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要逃走！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.39,0:10:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.44,0:10:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個叫黑笠的男人。。\N恐怕跟小生一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.38,0:10:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是以前幕府末年的殺人者吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.80,0:11:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是怎麼一回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.31,0:11:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不好的預感。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.38,0:11:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身。。身體動不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.89,0:11:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃了可不行我拔了一次劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.09,0:11:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論是哪一位都要被我殺死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.49,0:11:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不這樣的話就沒有趣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.47,0:11:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙要做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.88,0:11:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還可以動嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.78,0:11:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像不是一般的螻蟻之輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.05,0:11:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想讓我先砍哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.85,0:12:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手嗎。。頭嗎。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.69,0:12:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二階堂平法心之一方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.72,0:12:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另一種名稱居縮之術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.80,0:12:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.20,0:12:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幕府末年在京都有一個傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.30,0:12:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用眼睛發出來的氣\N來跟敵人戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.24,0:12:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使對手沒辦法移動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.91,0:12:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是善於使用心之一方的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.01,0:12:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,浮浪殺人者鸛堂刃衛！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.52,0:12:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也聽說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.92,0:12:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使用飛天劍流的傳說中的志士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.09,0:12:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左邊臉頰\N有大的十字傷口的殺人者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.49,0:12:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村拔刀齋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.13,0:12:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.96,0:12:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼有趣\N已經好久不曾有過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.26,0:12:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能跟拔刀齋見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.33,0:12:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像回到那懷念的幕府時代。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.47,0:12:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因金錢跟權力而腐敗的豬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.71,0:12:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管怎樣都可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.27,0:12:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經把目標改成你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.51,0:13:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來。最強的維新志士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.15,0:13:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.95,0:13:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心之一方是意志跟意志的勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.49,0:13:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要擁有跟你相同的劍氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.46,0:13:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就不會被制住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.40,0:13:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幕府末年殺了很多的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.43,0:13:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是為了要看到血而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.87,0:13:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不分敵人或同伴。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.37,0:13:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.74,0:13:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在是和平的時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.38,0:13:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日常中殺人的幕府時代\N已經結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.98,0:13:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了你自己覺醒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.35,0:13:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是不是聽錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.55,0:13:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被歌頌成\N非常冷血的殺人者拔刀齋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.19,0:13:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心已經不是殺人者了
