Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.57,0:15:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到那時侯給我回到以前的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.31,0:15:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去吧。回到冷血的殺人者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.35,0:15:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想殺的\N是那幕府末年的拔刀齋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.85,0:15:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刃衛！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.70,0:15:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畜生！那混蛋
