Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.84,0:15:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次是你成為目標了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.51,0:15:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係，應該說是個好時機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.98,0:15:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你。。你從一開始就猜測會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.51,0:15:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才接受拜託的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.68,0:15:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許正如那傢伙所說的\N也說不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.95,0:15:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的小生恐怕贏不了那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.83,0:16:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是小生要打敗那傢伙。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.06,0:16:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幕府末年\N以殺人而存在的同志。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.77,0:16:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這對我來說\N是不可避免的一場戰鬥
