Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.23,0:16:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種年紀的姑娘\N不該讓我看到這種臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.80,0:16:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像昨天擔心劍心的事
