Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.64,0:17:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他或許打算\N要回到以前的殺人者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.28,0:17:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂。！你要去哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.08,0:17:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那還用說嗎\N當然是去找劍心啊
