Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.39,0:17:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想對他綁手綁腳的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.05,0:17:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黑笠跟一般的對手可不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.59,0:17:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心。劍心已經打算\N不回到這裏來了
