Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.87,0:17:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打倒黑笠後就會回到以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.34,0:17:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣打算去流浪了
